      "value": "  \n\n=== DEVELOPER ACCESS INSTRUCTIONS ===\n\n1. Configure AWS CLI:\naws configure set aws_access_key_id AKIA6OM2PM4O5J6LZB25\naws configure set aws_secret_access_key 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\naws configure set region eu-west-2\n\n2. Update kubeconfig:\naws eks update-kubeconfig --region eu-west-2 --name innovatemart-eks\n\n3. Test access (read-only):\nkubectl get pods -n retail-store\nkubectl get services -n retail-store\n\n4. Developer can only view resources, not modify them.\n\n",
